Brief comments on your lst page:

 YES, I AGREE:
Don't use the term 'transient' to refer to all DIASources. This causes
confusion and is inconsistent with the usual meaning of transient as
impermanent astrophysical source, lasting only for a short time. The
term transient alert will also need to be changed.

YES:
